  "title" : "Find TODO tags in Eclipse",
  "body" : "<p>When I used Eclipse to add unimplemented methods to a Java class to fix an error, methods were auto-generated and include <code>// TODO Auto-generated method stub</code></p>\n\n<p>Is there an easy way to view all methods which contain this comment? Some sort of menu option?</p>\n"
